      "comment": "NICHOLASVILLE (1) is a talented dog who is a winner of eight races but missed the frame last time when sixth at this track (20.14). Can atone. UNTAMED VELOCITY (6) ran below her best last time finishing eighth (22.67) over 390m at this track in a Grade 4/5. Has a strong winning record at this journey. Hard to knock her form from this box, unbeaten in two starts. Likely to be about the money. NINA SIYAN (5) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish third (19.82) at this track in a Grade 5 over 352m. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from three starts. Leading chance. DISCO ETHICS (4) cannot be underestimated.",
